aces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能跟足正常程序出返七舊水畀佢會麻煩到好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf73be1ece2e1059bfe8e5a0b1a5e378c1c5de4","tid":460972,"uid":145365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:29:27.000Z","msg":"升沙展又炒撚埋 抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e8c7d90c04fb540da7b870bd5633958e60968a","tid":460972,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:30:25.000Z","msg":"覺得呢個故仔超假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2ea00f487fa64bbc0f26a3098e7ff5cd460a49","tid":460972,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:31:12.000Z","msg":"識玩"},{"pid":"c55c50b4b33ab41a07c25aa218209c142f368670","tid":460972,"uid":13343,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個上司點解要私了?<br />\n正常人唔會帶埋錢去打工<br />\n究竟有乜理由要咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能跟足正常程序出返七舊水畀佢會麻煩到好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能嗰阿頭自己或下屬做錯野/做漏野<br />\n跟住過咗正常追溯期<br />\n<br />\n如果要date back要 驚動更高層<br />\n覺得麻煩 / 影響自己仕途<br />\n<br />\n做得幫辦嗰d都 幾皮野up<br />\n七舊水跌少少當唔好畀壞印象上司睇<br />\n賭少場波/馬 已經係返到<br />\n<br />\n（如果件事真係咁簡單嘅話）"},{"pid":"7c8cffbe291a9209957fe61f964d40b9f7a88228","tid":460972,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:31:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男事主後來調往觀塘警署繼續投訴，情緒偶有波動，後來在晉升沙展面試中又落弟，不滿情緒更深。至近日他抗議行動升級，在警署內跪地舉牌向指揮官「道歉」，有人覺得他此舉可能確是希望真誠道歉，但亦同袍覺得可能有抗爭的意味。<br />\n<br />\n有警界消息聲稱，鑑於涉事高級警員情緒不穩，有警區高層早前已決定暫時不讓該高級警員佩槍，本報正向警察公共關係科查詢事件。</blockquote><br />\n步步高都係比黑警老屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731ec3a0b4aecffff37fdb2832e6b76c9bfffaea","tid":460972,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:32:57.000Z","msg":"唔係申冤咩"},{"pid":"c22d4c51956428ed89cbcad4996fc572096357ff","tid":460972,"uid":39215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:33:06.000Z","msg":"捽甩佢"},{"pid":"5ec7cd16476a8337ae9ea967638754e16ad31a54","tid":460972,"uid":59898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 警犬智力有問題"},{"pid":"029da77f8aef218cd08eaee1c0b73bfceb68aaf5","tid":460972,"uid":21480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:34:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebb74819e1cab01d50a2c4610562edf919d2a1f7","tid":460972,"uid":51717,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:37:17.000Z","msg":"無論真定假，有一點好奇怪<br />\n既然咁硬頸覺得自己無錯，無理由寫sorry sir........<br />\n你有無見過工人追欠薪，唔寫有汗出無糧出<br />\n反而寫 對唔住 老細<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e310551cf61c88d98798a8574c55e5d9d3b8c0","tid":460972,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爛鬼柴都叫高級警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁應該叫咩？做咩姐你"},{"pid":"98087353ac6a8fede71ae552529cb34db68243c4","tid":460972,"uid":52048,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解上司錯要講sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢覺得佢搞到上司 <br />\n上司就報復搞到佢升唔到職<br />\n所以 Say Sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4122db255f912289c097d7184b78ffa11a9cb9e7","tid":460972,"uid":232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"有成為第二個步步高嘅潛質<br />\n所以即刻收左佢支槍"},{"pid":"4b5d21e